{"type":"info-page","slug":"ijs/subscriptions","journal":"ijs","canonical":"https://www.sgmjournals.org/ijs/subscriptions","title":"IJSEM -- Subscriber Help & Services","bodyHtml":"<a name=\"top\" id=\"top\"></a>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/\"></a> \n        <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n          <tbody><tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"75\" nowrap=\"\"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td valign=\"bottom\">\n        <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#000000\">\n          <tbody><tr>\n            <td>\n\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"3\">\n        <br>\n        <hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" color=\"#000000\" noshade=\"\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table><font size=\"+3\"><strong>Subscriber Help &amp; Services</strong></font>\n  <p><strong>A <a href=\"/ijs/subscriptions/sample.shtml\">Free Sample</a> online issue is available to view.</strong></p>\n  <dl>\n    <dd>\n      <dl>\n        <dt><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></dt>\n        <dt><strong>ACTIVATE Your Institutional Subscription</strong></dt>\n        <dd></dd>\n        <dt><strong>How to use this site without a subscription</strong></dt>\n        <dd>Without a subscription you have access to Tables of Contents, Abstracts and more at no cost and without having to register.</dd>\n        <dt><strong><a href=\"#online-manage\">Managing your Subscription to IJSEM Online</a></strong></dt>\n        <dt><strong><a href=\"#print-manage\">Managing your Subscription to IJSEM in Print</a></strong></dt>\n        <dt><strong>Any questions?</strong></dt>\n        <dt><strong>How to subscribe to IJSEM including prices for 2009</strong></dt>\n      </dl>\n    </dd>\n  </dl>\n  <p><a name=\"online-manage\" id=\"online-manage\"></a></p>\n  <h2>Managing your Subscription to IJSEM Online<a href=\"#top\"></a></h2>\n  <dl>\n    <dd>\n      <h2>Institutional Subscriptions</h2>\n      <dl>\n        <dd>\n          <strong>Problems?</strong> Please read:<br>\n          Frequently Asked Questions about Institutional Subscriptions\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          Send us <a href=\"/ijs/cgi/feedback\">Feedback</a> if you're unable to access the full text and your institution has a subscription to IJSEM <strong><font color=\"#A70716\">ONLINE</font></strong>.\n          <p><strong>Account Administrator Only:</strong></p>\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          How to view or change your Subscription Information\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          What to do if you forget your Subscriber Reference Number\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          How to change the administrator User Name and/or Password\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          What to do if you forget the administrator User Name and/or Password\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          View Your Institutional Usage Reports\n        </dd>\n      </dl>\n      <p></p>\n      <dl>\n        <dt><strong>If you have questions related to your subscriptions, please contact the SGM Journal Sales office.</strong></dt>\n        <dd>\n          Office hours are 9 AM to 5 PM <font color=\"red\">UK time</font>.<br>\n          <strong>Society for General Microbiology</strong><br>\n          Marlborough House, Basingstoke Road<br>\n          Spencers Wood, Reading RG7 1AG<br>\n          +44 (0)118 988 1814<br>\n          +44 (0)118 988 5656<br>\n          <span id=\"em0\">sgmjournals{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n\n        </dd>\n      </dl>\n    </dd>\n  </dl>\n  <p><a name=\"print-manage\" id=\"print-manage\"></a></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <h3>Managing your Subscription to IJSEM in Print<a href=\"#top\"></a></h3>\n  <dl>\n    <dt>Change of mailing address for the print journal</dt>\n    <dd>\n      Send email to <span id=\"em1\">sgmjournals{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n       and include the journal title, your subscriber number, OLD ADDRESS and new address. Please allow 4 weeks for the change of address to take effect.\n    </dd>\n    <dt>Report of missing issues for the print journal</dt>\n    <dd>\n      Send email to <span id=\"em2\">sgmjournals{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n       and include the journal title, your subscriber number and missed issue volume and part number. Please allow up to 10 weeks for receipt of the replacement issue, depending on where you are.\n    </dd>\n    <dt><strong>Prices and ordering information</strong></dt>\n  </dl>\n  <p></p>\n  <hr noshade=\"\" align=\"left\" width=\"450\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td width=\"75\" nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"375\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\